              "text": "The last Lynnwood-bound 2 Line train serving all stations will depart from Downtown Redmond Station at 10:30 p.m., reaching Lynnwood City Center Station at 11:48 p.m.  \r\n\nThe last Redmond-bound 2 Line train serving all stations will depart Lynnwood City Center at 9:16 p.m., reaching Downtown Redmond Station at 10:33 p.m. \r\n\nShuttle buses between South Bellevue Station and Overlake Station will run every 10 - 15 minutes.  \r\n\n\r\nAffected stops: \r\n\nOverlake Village\r\n•\tTo Lynnwood:  152nd Ave NE & Da Vinci Ave NE\r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond:  152nd Ave NE & NE Shen St\r\n \r\nBel-Red\r\n•\tTo Lynnwood: 132nd Ave NE & NE Spring Blvd\r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond: 132nd Ave NE & NE Spring Blvd\r\n \r\nSpring District\r\n•\tTo Lynnwood: 120th Ave NE & NE Spring Blvd\r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond: 120th Ave NE & NE Spring Blvd\r\n \r\nWilburton\r\n•\tTo Lynnwood:  NE 8th St & 118th Ave NE\r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond:  NE 8th St & NE 116th Ave NE\r\n \r\nBellevue Downtown \r\n•\tTo Lynnwood: 110th Ave NE & NE 6th St\r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond: 110th Ave NE & NE 6th St\r\n \r\nEast Main\r\n•\tTo Lynnwood: 112th Ave SE & SE 300 Block\r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond:  112th Ave & SE 300 Block\r\n \r\nSouth Bellevue \r\n•\tTo Lynnwood: South Bellevue Sta – Bay 1 \r\n•\tTo Downtown Redmond: South Bellevue Sta – Bay 3 \r\n\n ",
